Package: salesforecastr
Title: Sales Forecasting with Time Series Models
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Alejandro", "Vargas", , "alejandrovargasauger@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A package for sales forecasting using time series models. It provides tools for data preparation, model fitting, and evaluation, with a focus on ease of use and flexibility.
